trans-unit.source: Angular 2 Seed is a starter project that implements best practices in coding, building and testing Angular 2 apps.
trans-unit.target: Angular 2 Seed est un kit de démarrage qui implémente les bonnes pratiques, la compilation et le testing des application Angular 2.
